CMSC 161 
Interactive Computer Graphics (3)  
Graphics systems software and hardware, 2D drawing algorithms, geometrical transformations, surface modelling, 3D viewing, visible surface determination algorithms, reflection and illumination models, shading models for polygons, color theory, ray tracing, animation  
5 hrs (2 class, 3 lab)  
PR. CMSC 123 or COI  
(1,2) 
